    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024580/extras/5357f3cc19f066cb2d6a9c1c4ef35488.poster.avif?t=1721146556\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024580/extras/5357f3cc19f066cb2d6a9c1c4ef35488.webm?t=1721146556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024580/extras/5357f3cc19f066cb2d6a9c1c4ef35488.mp4?t=1721146556\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《黎明杀机：Tomb Raider》带来一个全新逃生者<strong>劳拉·克罗夫特</strong>，她拥有三个专属技能：矫健身手、求生欲和老本行。购买此DLC可解锁一个<strong>专属护符：登山斧</strong>。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >劳拉·克罗夫特</h2>记忆中，树枝撕裂肌肤，湍急的水流灌进肺部。死里逃生的经历，以及更多即将到来的危险。无论是面对超自然的险境还是大自然的极限挑战，劳拉·克罗夫特都是生存本能的化身。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024580/extras/01be5f76914393f271750e4c432b3eaf.avif?t=1721146556\" width=616 height=207 /></span><br><br>劳拉·克罗夫特拥有<strong>3项专属技能。</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >矫健身手</h2>健康状态下，你可以更快翻越，成功翻越后会经历冷却。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >求生欲 </h2>当你打开箱子并净化或祝福图腾后，求生欲在本场对局中生效。从这一刻开始，每当你要尖叫时，改为显示杀手气场。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >老本行 </h2>每次打开或翻找箱子时，获得一层印记（至多为6层）。完成一次完美检定，会消耗印记，同时减少修理发电机所需总进度。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024580/extras/070951dc41a234adfb99bac1d124fc2d.avif?t=1721146556\" width=616 height=207 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >章节专属护符：登山斧</h2>《Tomb Raider》章节包含一个DLC专属物品，<strong>登山斧</strong>。请注意，此物品无法单独购买。<br><br><i> 有些地方永远都不该被探索。</i>",
